{"tid":1351641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所首披露鄭若驊持安樂工程股份","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T07:46:15.000Z","uid":81228,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"758a664a31a43d3f8d72dba0fa20cc4d3e8c1f8d","tid":1351641,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1563810176_EH-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1563810176_EH-1280w.jpg&h=ff22bd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊疑未有申報利益！據聯交所權益披露資料顯示，鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶旗下的安樂工程(1977)，鄭若驊以配偶身份，於該股本月12日上市當日，被視為與潘樂陶共同持有安樂工程8.89億股或63.48%股份，以該股今日收市價1.19元計，市值約10.58億元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1563810021_yP-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1563810021_yP-1280w.png&h=4d8c02cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於安樂工程招股書從未披露鄭若驊為股東，於主要股東顯示，潘樂陶透過信託私人持有該公司63.48%股權，亦未有顯示鄭若驊以配偶或其他身份持有股份。據政府公布的行政會議官守議員場的個人申報利益顯示，鄭若驊在去年7月1日填寫的申報表，在應申報其本人或連同配偶或子女持有上市和非上市公司，而且佔已發行股份1%或以上，必須申報的公司，並未包括安樂工程在內。<br />\n<br />\n不過，律政司新聞秘書回覆傳媒查詢時稱，鄭若驊的股權屬於「當作持有的權益」，並不代表司長實際持有或擁有實際利益，亦沒有股息權和不享有作為股東的權利，司長無權處理所提及的股份，因此不需要申報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%A6%96%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E6%8C%81%E5%AE%89%E6%A8%82%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD-181539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2589%2580%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BD-181539&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn22a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=39a9dd8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%A6%96%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E6%8C%81%E5%AE%89%E6%A8%82%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD-181539</a>"},{"pid":"ffff92bae673045508afc105c53a42b2d0ea58c3","tid":1351641,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a2f47dcf8985fcc206e42c1620db38cced70d8","tid":1351641,"uid":268094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"俾個機會佢下台"},{"pid":"386f49f1b6f167d2e0aac18097a4a6279ce059f4","tid":1351641,"uid":43082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2b93d650d8fe60d52f93258a2f717cba9474dfe1","tid":1351641,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"《連登已被五毛滲透 拉緊風向去內鬥》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351639</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e79bcf2de5fc8d801663b5f94245885eb0b6f724","tid":1351641,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"俾10億安家費你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73c0ff1c7bbee7172cfa71b2f672bd57ad033d4","tid":1351641,"uid":134323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"自己話自己不需要申報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e02773e5b79eec6cc839499282fd78c224323d4","tid":1351641,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"595e1b419acc9d5b365c7fbc505cb894ebe75b3b","tid":1351641,"uid":62167,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"其實ICAC一早廢左"},{"pid":"cd8b5d3f89234f991473e23344de5b35839cba85","tid":1351641,"uid":17890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ce340807e34cbe316ffe23052b2a6e28b2144dd","tid":1351641,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教我搵錢唔該"},{"pid":"5f3608868434040991c53a0941010f2c17e58268","tid":1351641,"uid":194718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"出哂風送佢下台"},{"pid":"fa332c50aeaf293878c77b1d5bfe39b1bb54048f","tid":1351641,"uid":36113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"波都打撚爆佢"},{"pid":"3e4a178b9d5d54a110ce78b7276942336729f402","tid":1351641,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"報icac"},{"pid":"516dad69f75d68248d14e4ae178d7da3278f747a","tid":1351641,"uid":30593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634a000f648c39949dffe66ecc1a683b3b4f85ce","tid":1351641,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d67d179782eb4bf9163333f0658cedfedab2d0ee","tid":1351641,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:20:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>鄭若驊申報　信託持有安樂股權</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190723/s00258/0db47002e237fa0205c6ae36ae90092d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190723%2Fs00258%2F0db47002e237fa0205c6ae36ae90092d.jpg&h=1917a117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】律政司長鄭若驊老公潘樂陶，早排成功安排旗下安樂工程（1977）上市，司長向聯交所申報，因應佢係潘生配偶，佢喺潘樂陶旗下成立嘅信託被視為持有（Deemed to be interested）潘生所擁有嘅安樂約63.48%股份權益。即係第日一個萬一唔好彩離婚，潘生啲股份，司長應該都有得分㗎。<br />\n<br />\n不過就仲要因應信託嘅設計或婚姻協議等，因為其實有啲上市公司老闆娘，都唔一定因為配偶關係有應佔股份權益。呢個申報，唔代表申報人一定要有股份，例如司長同潘樂陶屬夫婦關係，加上潘透過信託持股，而受益人之一若包括鄭司長，或鄭司長在信託內有其他角色，佢就要做申報。<br />\n<br />\n要講到上市公司老闆夫婦分家問題，小琴比較深印象係龍湖（0960）老闆娘吳亞軍，佢同前夫蔡奎離婚後，蔡奎分咗市值幾十億嘅龍湖股份，到今時今日都未沽晒，真正係打跛腳都唔使憂。<br />\n<br />\n小琴密語<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190723/s00004/1563820686876/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1-%E4%BF%A1%E8%A8%97%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%89%E6%A8%82%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00004%2F1563820686876%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25A8%2597%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn22a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=bffa2e1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00004%2F1563820686876%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25A8%2597%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A&h=d41104f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190723/s00004/1563820686876/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1-%E4%BF%A1%E8%A8%97%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%89%E6%A8%82%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A</a>"},{"pid":"b993480073987c3f55282b413e725320df0d29ee","tid":1351641,"uid":16185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"<code>我無嘢講</code>"},{"pid":"daa763aedfb0e77771db21404532aa4bab210ba3","tid":1351641,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:11:33.000Z","msg":"僭建 收錢 無利申<br />\n點解仲可以喺律政司<br />\n<br />\n阻阻大家 小弟嘅白宮聯署差15%咋<br />\n希望request國際人道救援/援助 人道監察<br />\n已經有八萬四千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn22a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=43b34ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0da36301a15c7218c3f6febc668696fa72d4a1f","tid":1351641,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係以為鄭若驊就解決到件事呀嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一日未有雙普選<br />\n一日都唔會退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa1ed25fc1cc38d3f2f2f5170d27f6a4ca06106","tid":1351641,"uid":126783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"推到人人睇到"},{"pid":"27e9f4fb0fbb2c69289462394abe72bfa95fbd86","tid":1351641,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b707fadd6c292d98a68a01b5a7a651fc7b76f02","tid":1351641,"uid":32215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da166d907395ca1c16f333fe9a